Flora Guerrero Goff bụ onye na-ese ihe, onye na-ahụ maka gburugburu ebe obibi, na onye guzobere Guardianes de los Arboles (Ndị na-eche osisi) na Cuernavaca, Mexico. Nwa nwanyị nke onye na-ese ihe bụ Jesus Guerrero Galvan, Guerrero bụ onye na-akwado ọrụ mmekọrịta ọha na eze na Mexico gụnyere nchedo nke Ọhịa Mmiri, isi iyi mmiri nke Mexico City yana mpaghara obodo ndị na-eyi egwu n'ime obodo Cuernavaca.  Dị ka onye na-ese ihe osise okpukpe ya na-egosipụta na-adịgide adịgide n'ụka dị iche iche, a kpọkwara ya ka ọ wulite ihe ngosi nke otu nwanyị, nke emere October 16, 2009, na Mision del Sol
na Cuernavaca, Morelos na mgbanwe nke nnukwu ego n'aka ndị nwere ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị.

Guerrero Goff eduziwo ngagharị iwe megide igbutu osisi site na ụlọ ahịa ọgwụ Farmacias del Ahorro na ebe ịzụ ahịa "City Market". Ọ gbara Secretariat of Communications and Transportation (SCT) akwụkwọ n'afọ 2018 maka ileghara ọrụ ogbenye na nke dị ize ndụ nke Paso Express na Cuernavaca anya.
